QBYRo |title=Ending the Subscribe to Pewdiepie Meme |date=28 April 2019 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=25 August 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=\"Zwiezen2019\">{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/pewdiepie-calls-for-end-to-the-subscribe-to-pewdiepie-m-1834365026 |title=Pewdiepie Calls For End To The 'Subscribe To Pewdiepie' Meme |last=Zwiezen |first=Zack |date=28 April 2019 |work=[[Kotaku]] |access-date=25 August 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Explaining why I REFUSED to play Minecraft - LWIAY #0085\"\n| align=\"right\" | 25 July 2019\n| PewDiePie explains his thoughts on ''[[Minecraft]]'', such as why he refrained from playing the game earlier during his YouTube career.<br/>The video is the 85th episode of PewDiePie's ''Last Week I Asked You'' series.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"LWIAY0085\">{{cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=leOb6ndKiWU |title=Explaining why I REFUSED to play Minecraft - LWIAY #0085 |date=25 July 2019 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=27 August 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=\"Hernandez2019\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/8/1/20727946/minecraft-youtube-popularity-memes-pewdiepie-grandayy-keemstar-minecraft-monday |title=Minecraft is having a big comeback in 2019 |last=Hernandez |first=Patricia |date=1 August 2019 |work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=27 August 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Marzia & Felix - Wedding 19.08.2019\"\n| align=\"right\" | 24 August 2019\n| A [[wedding videography|wedding video]] featuring PewDiePie and his wife [[Marzia Kjellberg]].\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"wedding\">{{cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7PIMiDcwNvc |title=Marzia & Felix - Wedding 19.08.2019|date=24 August 2019 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=15 April 2020 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Atad2019>{{cite web|last=Atad|first=Corey|url=https://etcanada.com/news/492032/pewdiepie-marries-longtime-partner-marzia-bisognin/|title=PewDiePie Marries Longtime Partner Marzia Bisognin, Shares Footage Of Ceremony|work=[[Entertainment Tonight Canada|ET Canada]]|date=24 August 2019|accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Best Week Ever. LWIAY #0089\"\n| align=\"right\" | 26 August 2019\n| PewDiePie visits the r/PewdiepieSubmissions [[Reddit|subreddit]] and reacts to fan submissions, memes, and reactions to his wedding and his channel reaching 100 million subscribers.<br/>The video is the 89th episode of PewDiePie's ''Last Week I Asked You'' series.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"LWIAY0089\">{{cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFzM-7_dSyE|title=Best Week Ever. LWIAY #0089|date=26 August 2019 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=15 April 2020 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Pardiwalla2019b>{{cite web|last=Pardiwalla|first=Tanzim|url=https://in.mashable.com/culture/6220/pewdiepie-did-a-meme-review-of-his-own-wedding-memes-was-he-amused|title=PewDiePie Did a Meme Review Of His Own Wedding Memes. Was He Amused?|work=[[Mashable|Mashable India]]|date=26 August 2019|accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Unboxing 100 MIL YouTube AWARD!!\"\n| align=\"right\" | 10 September 2019\n| PewDiePie reviews his past content up to him reaching the 100 million subscriber milestone. He additionally unboxes the [[YouTube Creator Awards|Red Diamond Creator Award]], given to him by YouTube for reaching the milestone, and announces a $50,000 donation to the [[Anti-Defamation League]] (ADL).\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"unboxing100m\"/>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Feigin2019/>\n|-\n| \"My 100 Mil Award BROKE! - LWIAY #0091\"\n| align=\"right\" | 12 September 2019\n| PewDiePie reacts to fan submissions on his subreddit. He also rescinds his $50,000 donation to the ADL, citing that he did not select a charity he was personally passionate about.<br/>The video is the 91st