DiePie's top 5 YouTube videos before his channel bites the dust |date=11 December 2016 |work=[[International Business Times]] |access-date=3 January 2019}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| align=\"center\"| 8.\n| \"Jabba the Hutt (PewDiePie Song) by Schmoyoho\"\n| align=\"center\" | 66.7\n| align=\"right\" | 14 September 2013\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"jabbathehut\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lxw3C5HJ2XU |title=Jabba the Hutt (PewDiePie Song) by Schmoyoho |date=14 September 2013 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=3 January 2019 |work=[[Scare PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | {{efn|name=jabbathehutt|\"Jabba the Hutt (PewDiePie Song) by Schmoyoho\" is a music video created by [[The Gregory Brothers|Schmoyoho]] (also known as [[The Gregory Brothers]]) and pairs auto-tuned voice clips with video footage from PewDiePie's content.<ref name=IBTimes2016/>}}\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | 9.\n| \"FUNNY GAMING MONTAGE!\"\n| align=\"center\" | 50.7\n| align=\"right\" | 28 October 2012\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"funnygamingmontage\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rc1XYAJCZ80 |title=FUNNY GAMING MONTAGE! |date=28 October 2012 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=3 January 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | {{efn|name=funnygaming|This video is an entry in PewDiePie's ''Funny Gaming Montage'' series, uploaded during PewDiePie's initial rise to popularity on YouTube. The video features gameplay of ''[[Amnesia: The Dark Descent]]'', ''[[Slender: The Eight Pages|Slender]]'', and ''[[Just Dance 4]]'', among other games.<ref name=IBTimes2016/>}}\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | 10.\n| \"Unboxing 100 MIL YouTube AWARD!!\"\n| align=\"center\" | 49.0\n| align=\"right\" | 10 September 2019\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"unboxing100m\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DYlesHOaPkY|title=Unboxing 100 MIL YouTube AWARD!!|work=[[PewDiePie]]|publisher=[[YouTube